task.summary: Implemented basic request-response for Lex bot
Added unit-tests for requests. Removed the classMain with a method main.
Added DynamoDB basic support with User-repository amd unit-tests for it.
Implemented add-method in the UserRepository. Added UnitTestFicture for real database access.
Implemented RepositoryFactory. Bot processing business logic extracted to the ShoppingBotProcessor class.
Extracted intent-processing logic to strategies, individual to intents. Supported first-last names in slots and session attributes.
Added Mockito framework to tests. Added ShoppingCartRepository.
Added User and ShoppingCart services. Business logic has been decoupled from repositories over servrce-interfaces.
Added logger to processors. Implemented storing of ShoppingCartItems. Supported in lambda more departments. OrderProducts test cases are mage as parametrized - to test all departments.
Added product entity (basic), its repository and service with unit-tests. Added copyright to files.
Added prices for products, individual to different units, with support of multiple unit-forms and synonyms.
